[{"Id": 1002399, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": "A person in his dream saw the Holy Prophet (s), very sad and the person ask him the reason of sadness and he said: that during Meraj he saw many believers being led towards hell and the reason was Imaan (faith). His Ummah was very weak in their Imaan and He recommended this Dua for protection of his Ummah and it will help them in the world, after death and also in the Barzak (resurrection). This dua is very helpful for a person who recites it daily between Maghrib and Isha Prayers…", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Ek shakhs ne Rasoole Khuda (s) ko khwaab mein dekha keh woh bohot ghamgheen hai, to us shakhs ne uski wajah poonchi. Us waqt Rasoole Khuda (s) ne farmaya keh; jab mai Meraj par gaya to maine dekha keh aksariyat Imaan waalo’n ko Jahannam ki taraf le ja rahe hai aur uski wajah kamzor imaan hai. Apni ummat ki hifaazat ke liye is dua ko padhne ke liye farmaya, jo unki madad farmaayegi is duniya mein, marne ke baad aur barzakh mein. Yeh dua mufid hai us shakhs ke liye jo isko rozana namaz-e-Maghrebain ke darmiyan padhe…", "UrduDescription": null, "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null,